a thing\nas a knee orgasm in the literature."}]},{"cues":[{"time":93000,"text":"I think the most curious one\nthat I came across"},{"time":97000,"text":"was a case report of a woman"},{"time":99000,"text":"who had an orgasm every time\nshe brushed her teeth."}]},{"cues":[{"time":103000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":106000,"text":"Something in the complex\nsensory-motor action of brushing her teeth"},{"time":113000,"text":"was triggering orgasm."},{"time":115000,"text":"And she went to a neurologist,\nwho was fascinated."},{"time":118000,"text":"He checked to see\nif it was something in the toothpaste,"},{"time":121000,"text":"but no -- it happened with any brand."},{"time":124000,"text":"They stimulated her gums with a toothpick,\nto see if that was doing it."},{"time":128167,"text":"No. It was the whole, you know, motion."},{"time":132000,"text":"And the amazing thing to me"},{"time":135000,"text":"is that you would think this woman\nwould have excellent oral hygiene."}]},{"cues":[{"time":139000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":143000,"text":"Sadly -- this is what it said\nin the journal paper --"},{"time":145739,"text":"\"She believed that she was\npossessed by demons"},{"time":148000,"text":"and switched to mouthwash\nfor her oral care.\""},{"time":151000,"text":"It's so sad."}]},{"cues":[{"time":153000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":154101,"text":"When I was working on the book,"},{"time":157000,"text":"I interviewed a woman\nwho can think herself to orgasm."},{"time":161000,"text":"She was part of a study\nat Rutgers University."},{"time":164000,"text":"You've got to love that. Rutgers."},{"time":166000,"text":"So I interviewed her in Oakland,\nin a sushi restaurant."},{"time":171000,"text":"And I said, \"So, could you\ndo it right here?\""},{"time":174000,"text":"And she said,"},{"time":175200,"text":"\"Yeah, but you know I'd rather\nfinish my meal if you don't mind.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":178339,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":179400,"text":"But afterwards, she was kind enough\nto demonstrate on a bench outside."},{"time":183000,"text":"It was remarkable.\nIt took about one minute."},{"time":185120,"text":"And I said to her,"},{"time":188000,"text":"\"Are you just doing this all the time?\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":191000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":192101,"text":"She said, \"No. Honestly, when I get home,\nI'm usually too tired.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":197000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":200000,"text":"She said that the last time\nshe had done it"},{"time":203000,"text":"was on the Disneyland tram."}]},{"cues":[{"time":205000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":207000,"text":"The headquarters for orgasm,\nalong the spinal nerve,"},{"time":210000,"text":"is something called the sacral nerve root,"},{"time":214759,"text":"which is back here."},{"time":216000,"text":"And if you trigger,\nif you stimulate with an electrode,"},{"time":219000,"text":"the precise spot,\nyou will trigger an orgasm."},{"time":223000,"text":"And it is a fact that you can trigger\nspinal reflexes in dead people --"},{"time":229000,"text":"a certain kind of dead person,\na beating-heart cadaver."},{"time":232000,"text":"Now this is somebody who is brain-dead,"},{"time":234000,"text":"legally dead, definitely checked out,"},{"time":236000,"text":"but is being kept alive on a respirator,"},{"time":238000,"text":"so that their organs will be oxygenated\nfor transplantation."},{"time":242000,"text":"Now in one of these brain-dead people,"},{"time":245000,"text":"if you trigger the right spot,"},{"time":247000,"text":"you will see something every now and then."},{"time":250000,"text":"There is a reflex called\nthe Lazarus reflex."},{"time":252072,"text":"And this is -- I'll demonstrate\nas best I can, not being dead."},{"time":258000,"text":"It's like this. You trigger the spot."},{"time":260000,"text":"The dead guy, or gal, goes... like that."},{"time":265000,"text":"Very unsettling for people\nworking in pathology labs."}]},{"cues":[{"time":268000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":269101,"text":"Now, if you can trigger\nthe Lazarus reflex in a dead person,"},{"time":274000,"text":"why not the orgasm reflex?"},{"time":277285,"text":"I asked this question\nto a brain death expert,"},{"time":281000,"text":"Stephanie Mann, who was foolish enough\nto return my emails."}]},{"cues":[{"time":284000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":285101,"text":"I said, \"So, could you conceivably\ntrigger an orgasm in a dead person?\""},{"time":290000,"text":"She said, \"Yes, if the sacral nerve\nis being oxygenated,"},{"time":292691,"text":"you conceivably could.\""},{"time":296000,"text":"Obviously it wouldn't be\nas much fun for the person."},{"time":300000,"text":"But it would be an orgasm --"}]},{"cues":[{"time":302000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":303101,"text":"nonetheless."}]},{"cues":[{"time":304581,"text":"There is a researcher\nat the University of Alabama"},{"time":308691,"text":"who does orgasm research."},{"time":310000,"text":"I said to her,\n\"You should do an experiment."},{"time":312120,"text":"You know? You can get cadavers\nif you work at a university.\""},{"time":315000,"text":"I said, \"You should actually do this.\""},{"time":317000,"text":"She said, \"You get the human subjects\nreview board approval for this one.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":320502,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":322389,"text":"According to 1930s marriage manual author,"},{"time":325000,"text":"Theodoor van De Velde,"},{"time":327000,"text":"a slight seminal odor can be detected\non the breath of a woman"},{"time":331000,"text":"within about an hour\nafter sexual intercourse."},{"time":335317,"text":"Theodoor van De Velde was something\nof a semen connoisseur."}]},{"cues":[{"time":339000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":341000,"text":"This is a guy writing a book,\n\"Ideal Marriage,\" you know."},{"time":343691,"text":"Very heavy hetero guy."},{"time":34600